 Madley's Diner

A simple restaurant ordering web app built with vanilla JavaScript, HTML and CSS.

The app renders the menu from a data file, lets users add and remove items, shows a running total, and allows the user to complete an order through a payment modal.

 Features
- Menu is rendered dynamically from JavaScript
- Add and remove items from the order
- Live total price update
- Payment modal with required form inputs
- Button changes to “Order completed” after a successful order

 Stretch goals implemented
- Meal deal discount
- User rating system with clickable stars


This project was built as part of the Scrimba 'Restaurant Ordering App' solo project.

